  • java.lang.Object
    • AccessAVLApp.BinaryTree<String>

  • Enclosing class:
    AccessAVLApp
    public static class AccessAVLApp.AVLTree<String extends java.lang.Comparable<? super String>>
extends AccessAVLApp.BinaryTree<String>
    AVL Tree keeps track of the height of the tree, balances the tree through rotations and is reposible for the program keeping its AVL tree properties while insert and searching or any other request There is also the opCount used to count every instance of an operation during a find or search and print that out
